
 
    1. To generate configurations for fwd-fp16 or bwd-fp16

       #> BUILD_FP16_CONFIGS=1 generate_configs fwd ./tmp.config      
       #> BUILD_FP16_CONFIGS=1 generate_configs bwd ./tmp.config      

    2. To re-order the configurations into the sequence that could be used by simple applicability validation

       #> reorder_configs ./input.config  ./output.config [fwd/bwd]
       #> cp output.config ../../config/igemm_fwd_gtc_gfx908_fp16.config

    3. To tailor configurations in one file with specific nxe and nxb (not used by generated configs)

       #> tailor_configs ./input.config ./output.config  


